We can pay for anything we want if you get rid of the capitalistic mindset. One day most jobs would already be automated and people are born to enjoy life and not work. Until that day comes, most human will just have to suffer this torturous period of our history. 
In the meantime, ask Trump or any Republican/Democrat about his defence budget, ask why we can afford the budget to invade other countries, ask why we can afford to give tax cuts to people who has so much wealth they don't need it, ask why other countries could give their people healthcare and college education and we seemingly cannot afford, ask why we're cutting fundings to our scientists, and ask why we even have people who don't believe in scientific facts in charge of our country.
